name: The Framing of Art - Exhibit C
description:
The Framing of Art - Exhibit C
The final piece of the series exploring the nature of reality from machine's perspectives (3 0f 3)

This particular piece is inspired and examining the concept of French artist Henri Simon Thomassin (1687 - 1741) in his work 'Portrait du Caravage' 


Music is an excerpt of Plastic Symphony No.11 in A#Minor by Siriosa's Post-Human Symphonic Choir
